@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - K
                   ====================================

                                Knight Tyme
                                ===========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Screen Jumper" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(24584,255) zxampoke(24585,255) zxampoke(45322,255) zxampoke(45323,255) zxampoke(41456,0) zxampoke(41457,0)"}           24584,255:24585,255:45322,255:45323,255:41456,0:41457,0

                         I don't know if this is of any use to anyone, but
                         it allows you to see the different screens by
                         using the controls.

                         First, select your control method (duh!), and
                         start playing. Go to Derby IV and ask for help.
                         (Derby is in the Transputer room, one screen to
                          the right from where you start).
                         The game will look as if it's crashed, but will
                         continue when you press fire. Then press down,
                         and the border will flash. Then use left and
                         right to change location and press fire to
                         continue.
@endnode
